I can never remember where we need to go to find that. Each time I need it I have to go find it too.
Someone should really add the links to the company wiki!!!!
We have a company wiki? Who knew!!
Yes! I had to do this the other day. Go to your team page on the intranet, and select 'Time Management', and then select 'Request Time Off'. That should get you there.
That's right! The intranet page! How did I forget that?
PERFECT... that is exactly what I was looking for.
I've gone ahead and added it to the wiki. Now we will have it in the wiki AND the intranet page. Should make it easier to find, at least. <shrug>
